  "intent": "Execute a multi-step blood extraction and PCR setup protocol: First, dispense 150\u00b5L of reagent1 from tube rack A3 to 20 wells (A1-A6, B1-B6, C1-C6, A12, H12) in a Corning 96-well plate. Add 20\u00b5L of reagent2 from tube A1 to corresponding wells in the first Bioplastics plate. Transfer 30\u00b5L of sample from tube A1 to each Corning plate well using fresh tips. Extract 5\u00b5L from each Corning well to corresponding Bioplastics plate 1 wells with individual tips. Distribute 20\u00b5L of mastermix from tube A2 to all wells in Bioplastics plate 2. Finally, transfer 5\u00b5L from each well in Bioplastics plate 1 to corresponding wells in Bioplastics plate 2 using individual tips for each transfer.",
